This paper proposes a Named Entity Linking system that can be trained from Wikidata only, which falls under the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Information Retrieval (IR) in computer science. The system also involves working with a large dataset, which could be categorized under Databases (DB). The use of machine learning techniques for training the model falls under Artificial Intelligence (AI) and the lightweight nature of the model could be categorized under Machine Learning (LG).
